[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      822[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **EHR integration is the hardest part of the entire project.** This example accepts a note as a string. In reality, getting clinical notes out of an EHR in real time requires HL7 FHIR subscriptions, ADT event feeds, or vendor-specific APIs (Epic's CDS Hooks, Oracle Health's SMART on FHIR). The integration layer is often more complex than the AI pipeline itself. Budget 40-60% of your implementation timeline for EHR integration alone. Connectivity to the EHR (Direct Connect, Site-to-Site VPN, or PrivateLink) must use TLS encryption and restricted security groups. PHI must never traverse the public internet between the EHR and AWS, even encrypted.
